      "title": "* -algebra-valued metric spaces and related fixed point theorems",
      "abstract": "We introduce the notion of the -algebra-valued -metric space. The existence and uniqueness of some fixed-point theorems for self-mappings with contractive or expansive conditions on complete -algebra-valued -metric spaces are proved. As an application, we prove the existence and uniqueness of the solution of a type of differential equations."
